fillTime.name: fillTime
fillTime.author: Markwhen
fillTime.description: Fills empty time between events. Each newly created event will have the `#available` tag. Only accurate to days (could use improvement...).

checkAll.name: checkAll
checkAll.author: Markwhen
checkAll.description: Checks all checkboxes in an event. Affects the event that contains the cursor, if any.
